; Driver fixture used by Commit 8 [Attach][Error] to drive a cavern
; failure. The unterminated *begin (no matching *end) and the bogus
; *data directive both make cavern bail out before solving, so the
; line-plot worker should surface a SolveError with Step::Cavern and
; the cavern log should carry the parse error text.
*begin Broken
*data normal from to tape compass clino
A1 A2 not-a-number 0 0
